question: Satwiksairaj Rankireddy is associated with which sports?
explanation: Recently, Indian men\'s doubles pair of Satwiksairaj Rankireddy and Chirag Shetty has clinched the $20,000 Vietnam Open International challenger badminton title at Hanoi by defeating the Thai duo of Trawut Potieng and Nanthakam Yordphaisong in three games  by 17-21, 21-9, 21-15.
